Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以欺负老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真想死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,足须小姐 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,足须小姐 好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,结果哥哥的内裤是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,表现的是
